#: ../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.14.rst:36
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The :meth:`~asyncio.get_event_loop` method of the default event loop policy "
"now emits a :exc:`DeprecationWarning` if there is no current event loop set "
